Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Lower San Raymundo Primary School in the Municipality of Jolo, Province of Sulu, to Sheik Salim Abubakar Primary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 237
An Act Changing the Name of the Lower San Raymundo Primary School in the Municipality of Jolo, Province of Sulu, to Sheik Salim Abubakar Primary School
Section 1. The Lower San Raymundo Primary School in the Municipality of Jolo, Province of Sulu, shall hereafter be known as Sheik Salim Abubakar Primary School.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: September 12, 1982
